{"tid":59702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邀英軍來港教步操 警被批惹火不智","createTime":"2016-12-30T00:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T22:26:57.000Z","uid":35790,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef527360a35faa338326067adb62f60f94257e7a","tid":59702,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:50:08.000Z","msg":"邀英軍來港教步操 警被批惹火不智<br />\n【東方日報專訊】【本報綜合報道】香港回歸近廿年，外電報道本港警方近日竟邀英國軍方人員來港，指導香港警察儀仗隊，報道甚至形容是次是回歸以來，英軍人員首度回港。消息證實，本月初邀請四名英軍儀仗隊人員來港教授步操，訓練五十名警隊人員，提升步操水平。有學者形容有關消息令人難以置信，指在此公眾對「港獨」熱烈討論敏感時刻，作出此決定甚為不智，批評是「惹火」及「無事生非」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/邀英軍來港教步操-警被批惹火不智-223015767.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%82%80%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E6%AD%A5%E6%93%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%83%B9%E7%81%AB%E4%B8%8D%E6%99%BA-223015767.html%23&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=87848f0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/邀英軍來港教步操-警被批惹火不智-223015767.html#</a><br />\n<br />\n回歸19年後<br />\n在中國領土仍然用英殖民地時英式步操<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889fbc203302cbaffc53122758271483f7525994","tid":59702,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:52:07.000Z","msg":"心繫皇家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a41f00f625546db94c45c1c6a522096c453eb68","tid":59702,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊幾時才回到正軌<br />\n改用中國式步操？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a799bfe07feedf2833403f9dc5ad251dba2637f1","tid":59702,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"請英軍又同港獨有咩關係？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow