i\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔跟解放軍仲唔係港獨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b67a283706cdf712eb17f591ae1bd7ffa12297","tid":59702,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://forces.tv/sites/default/files/styles/inline_image/public/Hong Kong Drill 2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforces.tv%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Finline_image%2Fpublic%2FHong%20Kong%20Drill%202.jpg&h=b6cfcfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&nbsp;提升香港警隊維持『儀式傳統"},{"pid":"046d2fc3f1dd4c56ee66194cfbdcd2c69290bc2e","tid":59702,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"香港警察就可以英軍學野<br />\n香港學生就要跟解放軍學摺被"},{"pid":"fb6fc2767386b9793d3c646dff4a73d297769492","tid":59702,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港警察就可以英軍學野<br />\n香港學生就要跟解放軍<span style=\"color: green;\">學摺被</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一睇見就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb2f3536e5968eca13fdf50be0cf9b40ecafc4a","tid":59702,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心繫皇家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女高級警司戴錯皇冠徽警帽<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20141018/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141018%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=811ab916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■關翠貞昨晨6時戴錯扣有皇冠警徽的警帽（左圖），4小時後已修正（右圖）。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處高級警司關翠貞昨在旺角簡報「清除障礙物」行動時大擺烏龍，戴錯一頂扣上港英年代皇冠警徽的警帽，四小時後再開簡報會才戴回洋紫荊警徽的警帽，她尷尬地說：「的確搞錯咗，𠵱家已修正番，唔好意思呀各位&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n認疏忽　稱無關警隊形象<br />\n<br />\n昨晨6時許，高級警司關翠貞向傳媒交代行動細節時，被記者發現她所戴警帽上的警徽竟是回歸前的皇冠警徽，其「大逆不道」的戴錯帽相片不久即在網上廣泛流傳，並引起網民熱論。<br />\n至早上10時，關翠貞再在旺角會見傳媒，當時她的警帽已扣回洋紫荊警徽。關翠貞尷尬地讚揚傳媒的觀察力，並說：「我自己疏忽，與警隊形象無關。」<br />\n48歲的關翠貞88年加入警隊任見習督察，97前晉升至高級督察，至去年升至高級警司，現於警隊人事部任職，丈夫亦是警務人員，育有兩子一女。現時警帽分為三級，普通警員至高級督察戴同一款；總督察的警帽帽邊加上一條黑色絨布，警司至總警司警帽則是不同粗幼的白色絨布；處長級的警帽則有不同的禾花區別。每名警員獲派兩頂警帽，警徽可除下方便清洗，回歸後警帽曾稍作改動，但大致保留之前的特色。&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20141018/18903911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20141018%2F18903911&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ec65eb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20141018%2F18903911&h=70575129\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20141018/18903911</a>"},{"pid":"884efdd5fa9bbfc1375406c38949ba16144fc6fa","tid":59702,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那真係好撚敏感 成身G點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7117c57b5167afe4161240a572b3eff40e6919","tid":59702,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d951f87074117337e7f07222c69240d3869ea